ActFarm Products Agencies Act
SubjectCanadian Pork Promotion and Research Agency Proclamation
PrecisCANADIAN PORK PROMOTION AND RESEARCH AGENCY PROCLAMATION in order to create the Canadian Pork Promotion and Research Agency and authorize the Agency to (1) promote the marketing and production of hogs and pork products for interprovincial export and import trade; (2) conduct and promote research activities related to those products; and (3) impose levies or charges.
